    "Html": "<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;I need a help to solve an intrinsic problem with the EventToCommand (or the binding in general). Suppose I have a MainView and a MainViewModel. The MainView has a ListBox like this one:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#a31515;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">&lt;</span>ListBox</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> x</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">:</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\">Name</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#0000ff;font-size:x-small\">=&quot;lst&quot;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;color:#ff0000;font-size:x-small\"> ItemsSource</span></span></span><span style