    "Html": "<p>Thank You for the reply.</p>\r\n<p>You right, it is much better to handle&nbsp;the&nbsp;SelectionChanged&nbsp;directly in the setter of the property binded to the &nbsp;SelectedItem, and it does solve my problem.</p>\r\n<p>Thank You</p>",
